    "title": "(test) Code Analysis Server",
    "version": "1.0.5",
    "description": "(test) Code analysis server for Python projects: CST editing, code indexes, semantic and fulltext search, refactoring helpers, backups, and quality checks (Black, Flake8, Mypy).\n\n### MCP Proxy (recommended)\n- Discover servers: `list_servers`\n- Discover projects: `list_projects` → use `project_id` for all project-scoped commands\n- Execute: `call_server(server_id=\"code-analysis-server\", copy_number=1, command=\"<name>\", params={...})`\n- Paths are project-relative (`file_path`); do not pass host filesystem `root_dir`\n- Long-running work returns `job_id`; poll with `queue_get_job_status` and `queue_get_job_logs`\n- Command schemas: `help(server_id=\"code-analysis-server\", command=\"<name>\")`\n\n### Direct API\n- OpenAPI document: `GET /openapi.json` (HTTPS/mTLS per `server` and `registration` in this config)\n- JSON-RPC command execution as described in the OpenAPI schema"
  },
